beer.beer_description:
In true Bracket fashion we used copious amounts of Motueka and Citra hops in every format we could get our hands on to bring you a beautifully balanced IPA worthy of a birthday release. You'll get bright crushed citrus and a unique 'green capsicum' character, that our head brewer Mike loves, from the early-harvest Motueka, along with sweet lemonade and ripe mango notes from the Citra.

As a lot of you will know we've been dialling in a few things to level up our hazies over the past few months and Stop Hustling is the cumulation of all that hard work. So this one's for you guys, thanks for 5 amazing years.

items.checkin_comment: Sure things don’t come much surer than a Bracket Mot/Citra IPA. Dense yellow clay colour but the palate feels lean and refreshing, zesty lime juice and a dash of orange. Gentle herbal bitterness too, a class act but not if you want sweet fruit salad.
